{"number":4,"verseCount":21,"verses":[[1,["Beloved, believe not every ",["spirit",["study-note-ref","a",[["Moro. 7:12 (12–17)","bofm/moro/7.12"],"."]]],", but ",["try",["study-note-ref","b",["GR test, prove by trial, discern. ",["1 Thes. 5:21","nt/1-thes/5.21"],"; ",["D&C 11:12 (12–14)","dc-testament/dc/11.12"],"; ",["50:31 (1–3, 31–35)","dc-testament/dc/50.31"],"; ",["129:9 (1–9)","dc-testament/dc/129.9"],"."]]]," the ",["spirits",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Spirits, Evil or Unclean","tg/spirits-evil-or-unclean"],"."]]]," whether they are of God: because many ",["false prophets",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Apostasy of the Early Christian Church","tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"],"; ",["False Prophets","tg/false-prophets"],"."]]]," are gone out into the world."]],[2,["Hereby ",["know",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Discernment, Spiritual","tg/discernment-spiritual"],"."]]]," ye the ",["Spirit",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Spirit of","tg/god-spirit-of"],"."]]]," of God: Every spirit that confesseth that Jesus Christ is come in the ",["flesh",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Flesh and Blood","tg/flesh-and-blood"],"."]]]," is of God:"]],[3,["And every spirit that confesseth not that Jesus Christ is come in the flesh is ",["not of God",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 50:32","dc-testament/dc/50.32"],"."]]],": and this is that ",["spirit",["clarity-word"]]," of ",["antichrist",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Antichrist","tg/antichrist"],"."]]],", whereof ye have heard that it should come; and even now already is it in the world."]],[4,["Ye are of God, little children, and have overcome them: because greater is he that is in you, than he that is in the world."]],[5,["They are of the ",["world",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Worldliness","tg/worldliness"],"."]]],": therefore speak they of the world, and the world heareth them."]],[6,["We are of God: he that knoweth God ",["heareth",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 8:47","nt/john/8.47"],"; ",["13:20","nt/john/13.20"],"; ",["D&C 1:38 (14, 37–38)","dc-testament/dc/1.38"],"; ",["29:7","dc-testament/dc/29.7"],"; ",["84:36 (35–39)","dc-testament/dc/84.36"],"."]]]," us; he that is not of God heareth not us. Hereby ",["know",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Discernment, Spiritual","tg/discernment-spiritual"],"."]]]," we the ",["spirit",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Holy Ghost, Mission of","tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"],"."]]]," of truth, and the spirit of ",["error",["study-note-ref","d",["GR deception, wandering, sin."]]],"."]],[7,["Beloved, let us ",["love",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Love","tg/love"],"."]]]," one another: for ",["love",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Love of","tg/god-love-of"],"."]]]," is of God; and every one that loveth is ",["born of God",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Man, New, Spiritually Reborn","tg/man-new-spiritually-reborn"],"."]]],", and knoweth God."]],[8,["He that loveth not ",["knoweth",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 17:3","nt/john/17.3"],"."]]]," not God; for God is love."]],[9,["In this was manifested the love of God toward us, because that God sent his only begotten Son into the world, that we might ",["live",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 3:16","nt/john/3.16"],"."]]]," through him."]],[10,["Herein is love, not that we loved God, but that he ",["loved",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Thes. 2:16","nt/2-thes/2.16"],"."]]]," us, and ",["sent",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Authority of","tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"],"."]]]," his Son ",["to be",["clarity-word"]]," the ",["propitiation",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Jesus Christ, Atonement through","tg/jesus-christ-atonement-through"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Redeemer","tg/jesus-christ-redeemer"],"."]]]," for our sins."]],[11,["Beloved, if God so loved us, we ought also to love one another."]],[12,[["No",["study-note-ref","a",[["JST 1 Jn. 4:12","jst/jst-1-jn/4.12"]," No man hath seen God at any time, except them who believe …"]]]," man hath ",["seen",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 93:1","dc-testament/dc/93.1"],"; ",["110:2 (1–3)","